gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 118, Jazz 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeat the Jazz, 118-111. Devin Vassell led the Spurs with 31 points and six assists while Victor Wembanyama added 19 points, eight rebounds, six assists, and five blocks (21st five-BLK game of year, no other player has more than nine). Collin Sexton (26 points, nine assists) and Lauri Markkanen (25 points, three 3PM, six rebounds) led the Jazz in the loss. The Spurs move to 17-56 as the Jazz fall to 29-44.
